Preparation of ultrapure dialysate in Japan--clinical usefulness and short-term 
future.

Sato T(1), Kurosawa A, Kurihara T, Kurosawa T.

Author information:
(1)Department of Nephrology and Dialysis, Sumiyoshi Clinic Hospital, Ibaraki, 
