expected, and even the prolongation of life expectancy. By using ultrapure 
dialysate as substitution fluid for saline solution, a fully automated dialysis 
machine has been developed. Furthermore, if fully automated consoles can be made 
smaller in size, they will contribute to the widespread use of home 
hemodialysis.

